    "Structured state space sequence model (S4) S4s are an extension of discrete state space models, which are widely adopted in control engineering 41.",
    "Discrete state space models map an input sequence u to an output sequence y, through the learnable parameters",
    "and D 2 R 1 × 1, as follows:",
    "In other words, discrete state space models define a \"linear recurrence\": at any step k, the k-th element of the input sequence u k is fed into the model and used to update the hidden state x k and to generate an output, y k.",
